text: Gentarō (源太郎) is a Japanese male personal name, and may refer to: * Kodama Gentarō (1852-1906), Imperial Japanese Army general and Meiji era government official * Yamashita Gentarō (1863-1931), Imperial Japanese Navy admiral * Gentarō Ishida (1944-2013), Japanese actor and voice actor * Gentaro Takahashi (born 1974), Japanese professional wrestler Category:Japanese masculine given names
title: Gentarō
